Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:21.12,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Morni—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:11.39,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wakanalia, please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:13.63,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We must combine our strength
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to free the sun god, who's \Nbeen sealed in Amana Iward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.67,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You were exiled from \Nthe Country of Sound, Musico.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you save the world alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.38,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:30.38,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,She's not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.46,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawania! You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.75,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't leave you by yourself, Konacchine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.60,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wakanalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you also wish to take \Nback the Harp of the Muse?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:50.27,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but the Country \Nof Sound and I are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.69,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not concerned with saving the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:01.52,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see what \Nthe three of us can accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.91,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.83,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.75,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Taking the frog brothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi and Wien, along as companions,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they set out for the \Nfaraway land of Amano Iward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:26.97,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Cue the first song!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.93,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:29.83,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,There are no princes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.45,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I have magic powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.64,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to be frogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.60,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty long, Konatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:36.94,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there should be a lot more singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.49,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:43.06,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you just asking about magic powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.17,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll save the best for last:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana's grand masterpiece \Nfilling the whole auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.29,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:53.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,How's the song coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.38,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to start rehearsals soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.10,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's starting to take shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:01.70,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,It should be done this weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe by the beginning of next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:07.01,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't exactly call it a masterpiece, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:10.42,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll finalize the \Nscript by then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we can start full rehearsals next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.14,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:21.82,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11 \NWaxing and Waning
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:25.04,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered if it was getting a bit long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:25.94,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You could cut it by half.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:26.57,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,By half?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.08,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Choir Club Culture Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.08,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Beauties and the Frogs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.08,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Script - Miyamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.08,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Song - Wakana
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.08,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Other Candidates:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.08,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}-"Amigo! Amigo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.08,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}-"Hauoli"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.23,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.28,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If you put in some magic here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.41,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Choreography - Sawa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.41,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Set - Tanaka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.41,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Props - Wien
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.41,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Costumes - Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.41,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Stage Crew - Everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.41,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}(26 days to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this scene would have a faster pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.41,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by sets?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like drawing mountains and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,castles on plywood \Nfor the scene backdrops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.56,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll have to draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.70,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.30,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't do art!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I was told to never draw again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.86,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you even try?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:54.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Don't freak out. I'm not expecting much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.40,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It can be grade-school level, for all I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.61,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana is writing our song,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Sawa's doing the choreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:05.11,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We're all new at this, so \Nyou're {\i1}not{\i0} getting out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.29,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Capiche?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.07,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:10.41,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Great, then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.45,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,She got her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.25,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,She's leveled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:17.21,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful, Konatsu! I'm gonna do my very best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.00,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.68,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I've put together small figures before,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this will be my first \Ntime working on props.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.51,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Um, 'kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.81,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you'd use styrofoam \Nor styrene boards
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:30.83,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We need a picture of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for these things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.59,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh hey, did you bring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:37.09,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}How much would that cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.39,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:40.54,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, that depends on the materials...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.57,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sneak outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.53,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Radiant Melody
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.53,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Work-in-Progress (Confidential)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.09,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.53,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some parts don't quite fit yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.05,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,So it might change...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:51.38,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I just need a rough idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can start planning the choreograhy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:57.45,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Konatsu's nuts to make me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.95,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't show the others, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.00,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.88,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.28,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, please don't expect too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.97,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,It's no masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:11.55,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,This song came from both you and your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:14.10,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,All that matters is that you're happy with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.36,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Konatsu said grand and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's just blowing hot air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.65,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, writing a song's \N a lot harder
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:29.20,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,If Konatsu wasn't so determined to use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might've put it away by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.62,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,telling myself I'd finish it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.37,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,But now I want to write \Nsomething you'll all like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.33,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I think this \Nwill be my first
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and last time choreographing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.38,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.80,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,But first, I'll give Konatsu \Nsome embarrassing moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.68,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.48,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}White Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.60,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Welcome to the White Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:05.23,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Welcome to the \NWhite Festival | Music Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:06.86,Default,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:08.49,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.83,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Safety
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:22.49,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Are they building something over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.13,Default,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.33,Default,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The stairs are ten meters wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.64,text,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,I listened to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.46,text,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you wrote this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.32,text,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,I love it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.11,text,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Can't wait to sing it, so keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.11,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,Here's today's picture. \NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.70,text,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.70,text,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Doing my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.67,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I think I want live accompaniment, not recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.37,text,Room,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Music Practice Room Two
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.20,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.06,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be best to use some miniatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make sure this is what you'd envisioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:50.59,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they look so real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:54.17,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Good job! Carry on, Mr. Watson!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:58.43,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I also made some drawings of the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.76,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Good job to you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:03.76,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't drawn in forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I worked while reading manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.15,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,and it turned out better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.41,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what is that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:13.86,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,A forest and castle, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.69,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it upside-down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:19.29,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,That's the least of our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:23.51,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Never draw again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.63,text,Room,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Art Room
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:39.57,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, is the president here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:46.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We're all busy getting \Nour festival pieces ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:50.65,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,All I need is a rough sketch. That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll copy it to the plywood myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.91,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever painted before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:02.30,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How will you apply the paint to the plywood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:06.00,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can you actually reproduce \Nthe proper colors from a sketch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.20,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No worries there. She's got low expectations,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it can look like a \Ngrade-schooler drew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.09,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:40.53,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:42.95,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hamachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.61,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were in the art club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:47.60,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I want to become a manga artist
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and live the dream of \Nliving off royalties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.08,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for an artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:54.42,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You'd do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.64,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,I won't even shortchange you \Nby doing some paltry sketch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:58.64,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it right, all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.13,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.05,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,But on one condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.42,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,Okita is in your group, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:08.73,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,I'll trade my services \Nfor a picture of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.10,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:13.11,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you really are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.86,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's got the looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:17.87,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,Just her, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.96,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,No group photos or shots from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.53,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure her chest is visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.66,Default,Hama,0000,0000,0000,,You can take it with your phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but try to make it high-res.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:42.18,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.63,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.12,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.02,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.43,text,banner,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Welcome to the White Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:13.14,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shirohamazaka High School Culture \NFair White Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.34,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:32.16,Default,Princ,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.41,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Luxury Condominium Complex \NConstruction Project
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:35.34,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The project is moving to the next phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.32,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,To ensure that we stay on schedule,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need the consent of \Nthe teachers and parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:43.25,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That's your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.80,Default,Princ,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.60,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,And yet it seems preparations for \Nthe culture fair continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:53.06,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I... I haven't been able to tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.16,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you'd better take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:14:00.83,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm holding a special assembly \Nwith the teachers today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.94,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be speaking to the parents this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.65,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Any delay would be extremely detrimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.53,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Do not disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:29.78,Default,ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Until the vice principal comes—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ueno-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.01,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:41.81,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:45.36,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Would you accompany us during our \Nperformance at the White Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.97,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Why not Sakai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.35,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Our group is small,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she wants to sing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:54.08,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing a musical,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.39,Default,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}A musical?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we need someone to accompany us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:01.04,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, you're the only \None I could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.45,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:04.34,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.30,Default,HIro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time to \Nplay with these amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:10.46,Default,HIro,0000,0000,0000,,We have preparations of \Nour own to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.43,Default,HIro,0000,0000,0000,,This year especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:13.63,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:15.31,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.48,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, by this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our song's been selected \Nand we're rehearsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:24.63,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,But the vice principal hasn't \Ntold us what we're doing yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,With all the songs we have to perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before the festival, \Nyou don't have extra time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.86,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,It might be okay if \Nit's a song I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:36.09,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,What are you singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:37.96,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Something Sakai-san's writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.00,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Writing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.17,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.92,Default,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid amateurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:43.92,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We're not stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.79,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, you're way dumber,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you can't even pick a song yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:56.95,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,But the vice principal's \Nbeen acting so strange lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:15:59.43,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:04.85,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,She's like one of those time-travelling \Nrobot weapons you see in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:08.11,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Except now she's run out of juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:10.99,Default,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:31.95,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Afternoon, folks. Welcome to the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:33.82,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.85,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,If this is about that {\i1}thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to hear any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.96,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Um, right. My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.12,Default,Mahiru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.11,Default,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Cut the chatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in your groups and do your exercises!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.34,Default,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:17.58,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Everbody's too relaxed, \Nwith the vice principal absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.47,Default,Ootani,0000,0000,0000,,She's not showing up again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.74,Default,HIro,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do this on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:27.27,Default,Ootani,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.91,Default,Ootani,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be here again? \NThat's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:32.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a different club, \Ncompared to when I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:52.42,Default,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, we haven't finished \Nour basic routine yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.48,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:04.39,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,This year's culture fair \Nhas been cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.80,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:24.33,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,We will have to suspend new \Nstudent applications for next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.86,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,As you are aware, the declining birth rate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has led to an annual decrease in students.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.31,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,It's been extremely difficult \Nfor the school to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,secure funding in recent years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.86,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we arrived at this \Nconclusion because we care
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about our student body \Nabove all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:46.65,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I am overcome \Nwith sadness and regret,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but with your support,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:52.68,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:56.03,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,We will be setting up \Ntemporary classrooms on the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,school grounds immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.97,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,and classes will be held \Nthere starting next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}About the White Festival Cancellation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:05.41,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,The renovations to the main building \Nwill begin in the new year,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and preparations for the school \Ngrounds will also begin then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.58,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,We promise that all our \Nstudents will be able
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to attend their classes, \Nunhindered, up to graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, should any wish \Nto transfer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will do our utmost to support them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.64,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}White Festival Cancellation Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You're still doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.98,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.70,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have to study \Nfor your entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.45,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Now you sound like my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.19,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm everyone's mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:28.70,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:33.54,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you should keep \Nsinging, even after you graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:35.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.47,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Were you playing badminton?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.42,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.93,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.82,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like we haven't met up in forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.97,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we see each \Nother in class everyday...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.68,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Heading home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:52.77,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:56.36,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky Tanaka's got badminton, \Nso he doesn't have to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.98,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Not that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:00.30,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.78,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.59,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I finished the song!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:30.10,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I want us to sing the song \Nmy mom and I wrote, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.74,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,We might not be able to do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anything about our school shutting down,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.48,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a White Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:34.20,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I finished the song \Nwe promised to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:35.48,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:37.10,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to do this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:40.52,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 12 \NPiling Up and Rippling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:38.08,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:40.52,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, we're going to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
